title: Predicting AFC Teams Win Totals
description:
Kevin and Nora are joined by The Ringer’s Danny Kelly and NESN’s Doug Kyed to pick the over/under on each AFC team's projected win total.

Hosts: Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti
Guest: Danny Kelly and Doug Kyed
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
